You can install luban in different ways.

For luban users:
 * Install using easy_install

   $ easy_install -U luban


For luban developers:

 * Install using releaser
   Please read http://dev.danse.us/trac/luban/wiki/Install_using_releaser

 * Install from source directly
   Please read http://dev.danse.us/trac/luban/wiki/Install_from_svn
